<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbcdd8c30-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s4741"><num value="4741">§ 4741.</num><heading> Declaration of purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purpose of this subchapter is to strengthen the training and development of State and local government employees and officials, particularly in professional, administrative, and technical fields.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbcdd8c31-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/648/tIII/s301">Pub. L. 91–648, title III, § 301</ref>, <date date="1971-01-05">Jan. 5, 1971</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1916">84 Stat. 1916</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
